<template>
  <card-countries/>
</template>

<script>

import CardCountries from "./CardCountries.vue"

export default {
created(){
     fetch("https://restcountries.com/v3.1/all")
        .then((el) => el.json())
        .then((json) => this.informacion = json.map((el) => {
            return {
              nombreO: el.name.official,
              nombreC: el.name.common,
              bandera: el.flags.png,
              poblacion: el.population,
              capital: el.capital
            }
            
        }))
}, 
name:"ApiCountries",
  
    data(){
        return{
            informacion: []
        }
},
components:{
    CardCountries
}
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
